lly separate.\nWe observe $T_\\text{TRSB}$ to track $T_\\text{c}$, supporting the hypothesis of\n$d_{xz} \\pm id_{yz}$ order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Mar 2021 11:06:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-09"}
