ied by elasticity and elastic turbulence as well as (a recently\nsubstantiated) region of elastoinertial turbulence and the unfamiliar\ntemporally stable region for intermediate values of Reynolds and Elasticity\nnumber.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Mar 2021 11:05:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
